---
title: Sticky Chinese-Style Beef Noodles with Sweet Chilli-Oyster Veggies & Parsley
description: The perfect sauce is here, so make room in your pan (and your stomach!) for this Chinese-style dish where beef, veggies and udon noodles take centre stage. With a sprinkling of fresh parsley for a boost of flavour, you’ll be slurping your way to noodle nirvana in no time!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*We’ve replaced the pea pods in this recipe with green beans due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just
follow your recipe card!*
